{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775846346294,"sessionID":"ses_28750e038ffeZCFapVkU4R9AGj","part":{"id":"prt_d78b0ccd8001xv93kCsSnZXbwu","messageID":"msg_d78b0ba4d001jfyeEhIQm1mseI","sessionID":"ses_28750e038ffeZCFapVkU4R9AGj","type":"tool","tool":"grep","callID":"toolu_1f5da43bf59d4999804075ef","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"pattern":"AR-008"},"output":"Found 6 matches\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/pkg/workloadmanager/design.md:\n  Line 1: # AR-008: Sandbox GC 定时清理机制 (Sandbox GC Timing Cleanup Mechanism)\n  Line 3: - **AR ID**: AR-008\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/.sdd_prompt.md:\n  Line 3: AR: AR-008 — Sandbox GC 定时清理机制\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-008/delta-spec.md:\n  Line 1: # Delta Spec: AR-008 — Sandbox GC 定时清理机制\n  Line 9: - **AR**: AR-008\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/proposal.md:\n  Line 1: # Proposal: AR-008 — Sandbox GC 定时清理机制","metadata":{"matches":6,"truncated":false},"title":"AR-008","time":{"start":1775846346284,"end":1775846346292}}}}
{"type":"step_finish","timestamp":1775846346317,"sessionID":"ses_28750e038ffeZCFapVkU4R9AGj","part":{"id":"prt_d78b0ce35001zeZBZbo0ZV62aW","reason":"tool-calls","snapshot":"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114","messageID":"msg_d78b0ba4d001jfyeEhIQm1mseI","sessionID":"ses_28750e038ffeZCFapVkU4R9AGj","type":"step-finish","tokens":{"total":26128,"input":9290,"output":72,"reasoning":0,"cache":{"write":0,"read":16766}},"cost":0}}
